outputs.output_descr: The project aims to strengthen capacities within the public sector to effectively mainstream HIV and AIDS into planning and budgeting processes of different offices, ministries and agencies. It further supports implementation of workplace programmes across the public sector.

project_descr: The project aims to strengthen capacities within the public sector to effectively mainstream HIV and AIDS into planning and budgeting processes of different offices, ministries and agencies
project_title: Strengthening capacities for Public Sector HIV and AIDS
